cross: Catasetum Karen Armstrong x Catasetum Darkness

measurements.description: Ten male flowers on one 28-cm inflorescence; sepals lanceolate, burgundy, white picatee; petals dark burgundy, overlapping dorsal sepal; lip cupped, intense dark burgundy, speckled white centrally, waxy texture; column dark burgundy, anther cap ivory, triggers white; substance firm; texture matte.
